						               													<description>This set contains 26 cards for use in games set in the perilous Badzones of the underhive.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The cards cover a diverse range of Badzones Environments and the Events that can befall the unwary within them.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The six Environment cards define the nature of the Badzone battlefield, ranging from a fathomless Slump Sea to an Unstable Dome. The 20 Badzones Event cards make the battlefield even more perilous, assailing the rival gangs with such hazards as a Toxic Downpour, a Brainleaf Outbreak, a Static Storm or worse...&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The cards in this pack make generating which Environment and Events are in play a simple matter, and each features all of the special rules needed to keep track of its effects.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Badzones Environments snd Events can be used in conjunction with most Necromunda scenarios. The rules for doing so are presented in the Necromunda: The Book of Peril gaming supplement.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the back of the box&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
